@startuml
title Consul Viewer TUI - UI State and Navigation

skinparam shadowing false

state "Current Section" as Section
state "Current Focus" as Focus
state "Section Mode" as Mode
state "Selection" as Selection
state "History Stack" as History
state "Filters" as Filters
state "Sort Option" as Sort
state "Popup State" as Popup

[*] --> Section
[*] --> Focus
[*] --> Mode
[*] --> Selection
[*] --> History
[*] --> Filters
[*] --> Sort
[*] --> Popup

Section --> Mode : list / instances / links
Section --> Selection : selected row id
Section --> Filters : text + status + instance filters
Section --> Sort : per-view sorting

Focus --> Section : Tab / Shift+Tab
Focus --> Selection : Up / Down
Focus --> Popup : F1 / F6 / F7 / F8 / F9 / F11 / exit

Selection --> Mode : Enter drill-down
Mode --> History : push previous location
History --> Section : Backspace restore
Popup --> Filters : apply popup filters
Popup --> Sort : apply sort settings

note right of Filters
Text, status, and structured
instance filters are layered.
end note

note right of Sort
Sorting is stored separately
for each visible list mode.
end note

@enduml
